Meet Amanda

Building what I wished existed

"I saw how often women are given fragmented, oversimplified guidance about their bodies, health, and lives - and I wanted to create something more truthful."

Amanda Henry is a former Therabody Founding Team Member, wellness and brand leader, storyteller, and investor with over 15 years of experience building culturally influential brands at the intersection of wellness, fashion, and technology.

She spent nearly a decade helping scale Therabody into a global wellness brand - leading global PR, major partnerships, and women's wellness initiatives. Well, Honestly is the platform she wished existed: nuanced, culturally aware, and rooted in the belief that women deserve better.

Therabody Founding Team 2x PR Net Most Influential Cannes Lions Jury Angel Investor AfPC Advisory Council
